name: Dhanush V D Upadya
about: I was born in Bangladesh, grew up in New York City and went to school in Nashville, TN (Vanderbilt). I am super Desi when it comes to Cricket and Bollywood. I love to read and travel. Currently, I am working to grow Peloton and disrupt the fitness industry. My job is to find and hire the current and future bad-asses in the technology industry.
